id: hac-ak9g
title: "Make static quality, duplication, security, and pm integrity gates mandatory"
description: "Add deterministic Bun scripts and required CI coverage for strict ESLint, docstrings, jscpd, pm validation/health, ShellCheck, Trivy, dependency audit, secret history, CodeQL, coverage upload, build, package smoke, and release verification; document applicability and local parity."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[6]: ci,codecov,jscpd,pm,security,static-analysis
created_at: "2026-07-21T19:13:48.497Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T20:51:50.100Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-21T20:51:48.614Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 540
acceptance_criteria: One local quality command runs every applicable free gate; CI has required non-optional jobs; unsupported or inapplicable tools such as PSScriptAnalyzer are explicitly documented rather than silently claimed; branch protection requires the new contexts; docs explain exact local and hosted parity
definition_of_ready: "Existing workflows, package scripts, installed tool availability, and free GitHub feature constraints inventoried"
value: A reproducible non-bypassable production quality contract
impact: "Blocks duplication, documentation, type-safety, security, tracker, and coverage regressions before merge"
outcome: Required green quality evidence on every PR and master head
why_now: "Current CI lacks duplication, docstring, ShellCheck, Trivy, and pm integrity jobs and coverage upload is artifact-only"
parent: hac-n0ix
reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: high
release: 2026.7.22
resolution: "Added static, documentation, duplication, file-size, ShellCheck, PM integrity, Codecov, Trivy, dependency, CodeQL, package, changelog, history, and review-inventory gates; fixed fresh-runner PM bootstrap; required every new hosted context in branch protection."
expected_result: "All applicable free quality and security tools are deterministic mandatory gates locally and on GitHub, with strict master protection requiring their registered contexts."
actual_result: "Fresh-clone PM bootstrap passes; exact PR head is green; strict master protection now requires static-contracts, changelog, and Trivy alongside every existing quality/security context."
comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:19:14.143Z",codex-root,"2026-07-21 jscpd baseline against all 111 src TypeScript files: 70 clone groups, 527 duplicated lines, 4.36% line duplication / 5.17% token duplication at min 5 lines and 50 tokens. No exclusions or skip directives will be used; this inventory drives shared command/action abstractions and a zero-new-duplication mandatory gate while legacy clones are removed."
  "2026-07-21T19:39:52.792Z",codex-root,"The mandatory gate stack now includes strict ESLint and erasable syntax,100-percent source-file docstrings,jscpd ratcheting,300-code-line enforcement,ShellCheck,PM validate and health,Codecov,Trivy,dependency audit,history secret scanning,CodeQL,build test package smoke and generated changelog verification. PSScriptAnalyzer remains explicitly inapplicable because the repository has no PowerShell."
  "2026-07-21T20:36:04.464Z",codex-root,"Local aggregate gate passes: strict TypeScript and ESLint, 115/115 docstring coverage, jscpd 4.22% below the 4.36% ratchet, every source file at or below 300 code lines, ShellCheck, strict PM validation/health, Bun audit, and Trivy with zero high/critical findings. New hosted contexts will be added to strict branch protection after this PR registers them once."
  "2026-07-21T20:44:19.997Z",codex-root,"PR #60 is registering the new static-contracts, changelog, and Trivy contexts. After they pass once, strict master protection will be updated to require them and that exact protection state will close this task."
  "2026-07-21T20:47:51.001Z",codex-root,"Hosted static-contracts failed only on fresh-runner PM bootstrap: Git omitted five empty required directories and pm-changelog had not yet been installed. The gate now preserves those directories and installs the latest extension with telemetry disabled before strict validation."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:13:57.356Z",codex-root,PSScriptAnalyzer is inapplicable because the repository contains no PowerShell. Greptile is an external review integration rather than a local deterministic binary; it remains a PR review gate. All other applicable free gates must have local parity.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:51:45.431Z",codex-root,"Strict PM validation must be tested from a fresh clone: empty required directories and locally installed extensions can make a workstation pass while a clean GitHub runner fails. Preserve directory placeholders and bootstrap the latest managed extension inside the gate."
